*Robot Science & Technology* is a fairly new magazine, and I give it
my high recommendation.  Issues 2, 3, and 4 contain a series, "Popular
Micromouse Algorithms", by Tak Auyeng, PhD.  Lots of good info for
anyone interested in the IEEE Micromouse Competition.

